cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper discusses a framework for analyzing neural models for multi-task learning, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed framework involves communication between tasks, which is also relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also evaluates the proposed methods on tasks related to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE).
